      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个甘特图来展示项目的时间线。整体标题就叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"吧，时间格式用YYYY-MM-DD。",
      "elements_involved": [
